title: 15 James Bond 007 Audio Books - Ian Fleming - Kingsley Amis
description:
This is a compilation of James Bond audio books.
Ian Fleming and Kingsley Amis are the authors.
The MP3s are 40kbps, 22050Hz mono. Sounds fine, though.

I got this torrent from some other (lame) torrent site, and decided to upload it to The Pirate Bay. I removed some dead trackers from it and added thepiratebay trackers. Enjoy, and post comments about how much I rock.

-Necrocytosis
